data.description: Welcome to this beautifully maintained townhouse that combines comfort with modern living. Nestled in a desirable neighborhood, this home offers a perfect blend of convenience and tranquility. Two large bedrooms, each with its own private bathroom, provide ample space for relaxation and privacy. The master suite features a walk-in closet and an en-suite bath. Located  close to shopping, dining, public transportation, and major highways, making commuting and weekend outings a breezeBuyer's Agent must accompany their client for showing. HOA fee is $671 a month which covers the following: Cable, Water and trash, Exterior insurance so Buyer only needs to cover interior contents
